"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly uses the lmplot function within the map method of a FacetGrid. The lmplot function is a figure-level function and cannot be used in this context. Instead, the regplot function should be used for plotting within a FacetGrid.\", \"patch\": \"6c6\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g.map(sns.regplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n\"}"